{"tid":1424813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"早前有接仔放學 今後要接官返工","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:06:46.000Z","uid":300833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b4eab6d646f00dc09a1e2d4b5b29478bcc6806a7","tid":1424813,"uid":300833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"衣家次次去夢遊都俾popo打鑊金 無論佢popo點被人鬧 都繼續返工黎打我地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而班離地官日日都好似唔存在係香城甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗不如星期六星期日去班官既屋企叫佢返工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫佢地出黎返工開會 <br />\n好過我地班手足被popo 打完都覺得事不關己甘<br />\n<br />\n現階段既情況係我地班手足已經流左好多血 被拉左好多個  班官就係度廢嗡 因為佢地覺得唔關自己事 粒催淚彈又冇飛去自己屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衣家再去夢遊popo屋 無論幾勇武 都只係一身防禦裝備 唔通真係有一日popo會跪地投降叫大家停手 唔好再圍？ 或者我地班手足以身食彈會令入面班popo棄械投降？ 定係調轉會有軍火商俾ak俾子彈俾盾玩PUBG 咁俾手足攻入去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而最實際係夢遊去高官屋企 就要勞煩佢地出黎做野 甚至到popo要清場就順便令班高官索多幾啖催淚彈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議手足下次夢遊就去圍禮賓府 叫777聞下催淚彈 <br />\n繼續就去山頂政務司個度 叫佢地好好返工 否則返唔到屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要叫班高官感受到香港人唔係不合作 而係班官唔工作 <br />\n<br />\n一於接官返工！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d12043ba86a456c8cf681f8fb8a200435721697","tid"